            <description><![CDATA[Q: Whether the image/frame from VideoCapture is in BGR or YUV pixels format?]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Q: Whether the image/frame from VideoCapture is in <code>BGR</code> or <code>YUV</code> pixels format?
A:
VideoCapture will convert the image automatically to BGR colorspace.
you can disable this conversion (and receive YUV) by setting the CAP_PROP_CONVERT_RGB property to false.</p>]]></content:encoded>
